adviseScripts.text: Hey, Commander, when you see a lady, which place do you look first?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I want an honest answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Her face.
Her heart.

Hah!
I always knew you were a face guy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
Huh? No?
Then which part do you think is the most important?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Ugh! What a corny answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: How can you see a woman's heart at the first glance?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation about ideal types with Anis.
Should I take a shower before going to bed,
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: or after getting up?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I didn't go outside today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Then you don't need a shower at all.
Then shower twice!
Hey, I'm serious!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It's only proper to take a shower at least once a day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: That would be nice, but I'm afraid there is not enough hot water.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Hey, why don't I take a shower in your room?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I discuss body wash and shampoo.

As a Nikke, I've always got my hands full.
But sometimes, I have to wonder... what's the point of all this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
I can't find much joy in my work,
 but there's nothing else I can do.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Commander, what do you think I should do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Not everyone finds joy in their work, and that's okay.
You can try to find joy in your work.

Hmm... You're right.
A job is just a job, after all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Only a few geniuses can find meaning in their work.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Never mind. I just need to work hard. That's enough.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Joy... Joy...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Didn't that kind of thing go away a long time ago?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis tells me her tricks for slacking off at work.

Argh!!
Commander, I can't stand Liter any more!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Her constant nagging is driving me crazy!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: So what if I leave my dirty socks lying around?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Because she's the one who does the cleaning.
Socks? Where?
That's true, I admit...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: But I did pick up all my socks today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It may have been my fault in the past, but today I'm perfectly innocent.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Commander... are you really into that kind of thing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: If you... if you really want my socks, maybe I can show you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I discuss good socks.
Neon's crazy, I reckon.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: She's a firepower maniac.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: That's why she excels at what she does.
You shouldn't say that about your teammate.
I know, right? She's a complete maniac.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: But, in a way, I envy her. She has something that she's passionate about.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Even if it's something weird, like firepower.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I don't mean she lost her mind or whatever.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
And I also didn't mean... Pfft... 
How to put this...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Forget about it, Commander.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I discuss the definition of a "maniac".
Chocolate-flavored Splendamin, and chocolate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: The former is cheap and common, and the latter is expensive and rare.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: However, they have the same taste.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: So, which one is better in the end?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Chocolate.
Chocolate-flavored Splendamin.

Hmm... Really?
Your choice surprises me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Since different paths lead to the same destination, why bother taking the hard path?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: The path itself is meaningless.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Absolutely!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Since different paths lead to the same destination, I think it's wise to take the easy path.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: That's the only way to lead an easy life.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk about all the different kinds of chocolate.
Rapi is amazing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: She has suffered so much, but she's still so determined.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: She's so different from me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Sometimes I just can't figure out why we were put in the same squad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Your differences are what make you work well together.
You have many strengths as well.
Huh! So, it because we complement each other?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
That's good to hear!
Thanks! You've really cheered me up.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... After all, I don't want Rapi to hate me or anything.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Me? That's impossible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
How to put this?
I just live my life aimlessly.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
I have nothing to live for, but I don't want to die, either.
I'm like some kind of zombie.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Anis praising Rapi in a thousand different ways.
I've been talking in my sleep a lot lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
Last night, Neon woke me up
and asked me why I keep babbling on...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... Should I ask Mary for medical treatment?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Did you apologize to Neon?
Seems like you've been under a lot of pressure recently.
I don't even know what I should apologize for.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... Hey, wait a minute.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: What if Neon was lying to me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
You make a good point.
After all, times have been tough since we met.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Ah, please don't get me wrong. I don't mean I dislike being with you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I'm just under so much pressure.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I share some advice about getting better sleep with Anis.
How strange! My shoulder got stiff all of a sudden...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: But I don't think there is anything wrong with it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Maybe because your shoulder is too heavy.
... Anis, there's a person on your shoulder.

Hee-hee.
That's for sure. I'm confident about my shoulder.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
Commander, do you want to have a try?
Just once.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Waaaah!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text:
... Commander,
please don't tease me like that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I practice stretching out stiff shoulders with Anis.
Commander, this uniform I'm wearing...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It's a gift from my boss, Mustang.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Do you think it's a little bit...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Bizarre? Kind of.
You look gorgeous in it.
Is... that so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Should get something else to change into?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Ah... I may not have enough money.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anyway, if you really think so, then...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Feel free to look at it as much as you want.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I discuss fashion with Anis.
Commander, could I ask you...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: do you like boy bands and girl groups?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: No real reason, I'm just curious, that's all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I would literally die without them.
I don't have much interest in them.
You're that much of a fan?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: What group do you like the best? Spotlight or Dome of Eternity?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: They're kind of older, but have you heard of T.T.?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Hmmm... as expected.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I figured you would feel that way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Then, are there any other singers or celebrities that you like?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I have a lovely conversation about celebrities.
I found a wallet once before, and it ended up being a horrible experience.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Ever since then, I tend not to help others.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: How about you, Commander? Do you help others, or ignore them?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I can't ignore someone that is in trouble.
You should solve your own problems.
That's such a "you" answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I suppose that's how most people are actually. No matter how much the world has changed, that human connection still remains...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Sigh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I guess it doesn't matter all that much, since I'm not human.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: My thoughts exactly.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: In the end, you're the only one who can solve your own issues.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: So you might be better off not giving or receiving any help.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Still, that's an unexpected answer from you, Commander.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I converse about humanity.
Do you know how Neon, the spy who's obsessed with firepower, wears glasses?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Since she's a Nikke, couldn't she just swap out her eyeballs?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Why does she bother wearing glasses?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: They don't serve any purpose, and it seems like they'd be uncomfortable.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Don't you ever put down her glasses!
I'm not so sure myself.
Yikes, you surprised me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Why are you yelling all of a sudden?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Wait a minute, you're actually being serious.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I didn't expect much, but still...what a boring answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I should just ask her next time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ...Nevermind. There's no point in prodding any further.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk about vision.
You know Splendamin, the food we're always stuffing down?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: For a supposed "wonderfood", its name is so bland.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It might be better if it had a more mouth-watering name.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Juicy Perfecto.
Ultra Splendamin.
That's... a little better, maybe?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... I think it still needs some work.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Still, I appreciate you giving it some thought.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Sounds like some kind of supplement.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Folkwang will probably go gaga over it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk about the profound effect naming can have.
When we deal with others, we're always putting on different masks to suit different people.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: If we were to show them our true colors, would they be averse to it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: If you're gonna put on a mask, might as well wear a cool Ark Rangers mask.
You can't please everyone. Haters gonna hate.
I shouldn't have brought this up.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I feel the same way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It's impossible to be loved by everyone.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... I tried, but it didn't work out.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I have a long conversation about masks.
I feel weird saying this,
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: but I find the heat of battle kind of thrilling.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I can't believe I'm saying this, but I may be a warmonger of some kind.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: What's so surprising about that?
Your body is tricking your brain in order to survive.
What? You see me as belligerent?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Really? Haha, stop kidding around.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: ... Are you serious?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Right... adrenaline and all that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: That must be the reason.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It can't be just because I enjoy smashing things up, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I discuss one's mental fortitude during battle.
This is a bit random, but does it bother you
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: that I use your shower whenever I want?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Having a girl shower in your room must make you a bit uneasy, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Uh...
It really doesn't affect me that much.
Your eyes are starting to wander off...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: What's going on in that head of yours?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: You look like you're reminiscing about something euphoric! Cut it out!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I guess it's nothing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Good to hear.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk about shower supplies.
How are things going with Rapi?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: If you're going through a rough patch, just let me know. I can help.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: She can be a bit... fastidious.
I'll try to figure it out myself.
Rapi? No way, she's just thorough!
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: As long as you do what you're supposed to be doing...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Hmm... I said I'd help, but all I'm doing is defending her...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: So you're having a tough time dealing with her?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: No worries, I'm sure you'll be able to move past it. It's you after all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Rapi is very accommodating so if anything is ever bothering you, don't hide it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk more about Rapi.
Do you like dogs?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: A long time ago, I met a dog. It must have liked me since it bounded right up to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It was the first time I had ever seen that dog, yet it made a beeline straight for me...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: You must have felt uncomfortable.
You must have been happy.
Yes. I didn't really like it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I knew it didn't mean any harm. It just liked me is all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: But nevertheless, it did make me feel uncomfortable.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I suppose it's just hard to accept such blind affection.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Hm... Well...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I suppose so, but...
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It made me question why it was so fond of me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I didn't like how it just threw caution to the wind and ran right over to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I talk about animals.
If the world was ending tomorrow,
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: what would you want to do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I would complete my bucket list.
I would just sit back and do nothing.
You've got a bucket list?
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I envy you. I don't have anything like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I think I'd just sit around and take it easy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Same here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I don't have many purposes in life anyway, so I can't pretend to suddenly have some out of the blue.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: I'd just go about my usual routine and quietly wait for the end.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: It... feels nicer knowing that I'm not alone.
adviseScripts.speaker: Anis

adviseScripts.text: Anis and I watched a TV show about possible apocalyptic scenarios.
